snippet.title: Arcane Quest 2 Mobile RPG Game - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Arcane Quest 2 is a mobile videogame available on Android, Windows Phone and iOS (iPhone/iPad).
The game is a classic board game styled RPG inspired by HeroQuest and other games of this kind.

GOOGLE PLAY STORE:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nex.xquest2

WINDOWS PHONE STORE:
http://www.windowsphone.com/s?appid=2bd45b55-afc7-4ce9-a725-94ddeaf08c93

Arcane Quest 2 offical page:
https://www.facebook.com/arcanequest2

Nex Game Studios official site: 
http://www.nexgamestudios.com




Thanks to RavenDesign for the trailer template.
